The paper deals with image manipulation using natural language, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The proposed method involves the use of Generative Adversarial Network (GAN) and attention mechanism, which are popular techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also evaluates the performance of the proposed method on image datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
